          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "Here's the second question: Do all the numbers end in 0 or 5?"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "7, 12, 19, 23. None of them end in 0 or 5. Scale of 2 is the only one that works exactly. When you look at new data, which question do you check FIRST?"
        },
        {
          "type": "prompt",
          "text": "Which question should you check FIRST?",
          "tool": "multiple_choice",
          "options": [
